    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0.8em; z-index: 15; break-inside: avoid;\">A set of tinker's tools is designed to create small, inventive devices from omni-gel. Some examples include a motion sensor, a desalinator, a compass, a light source, or a small EMP device.</p>\n<hr style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: hidden; margin: 0px; font-family: BookSanity; font-size: 11.9811px;\">\n<ul style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 0px; padding-left: 1em; list-style: outside none; text-indent: -1em;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\">Type</strong>. Artisan</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\">Cost</strong>. 3,000 credits</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\">Components</strong>. Tinker's tools include a variety of hand tools, wires, scraps of metal, batteries, microcircuit boards, adhesives, paint, and a pouch that can hold up to 10 omni-gel canisters.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"benefits\" style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 800; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.458cm; line-height: inherit; font-family: MrJeeves; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 0.2em; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #58180d;\">Benefits</h4>\n<hr style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; visibility: hidden; margin: 0px; font-family: BookSanity; font-size: 11.9811px;\">\n<ul style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 11.9811px; line-height: 1.3em; font-family: BookSanity; vertical-align: baseline; margin-top: 0px; padding-left: 1em; list-style: outside none; text-indent: -1em;\">\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\">History</strong>. You can determine the age and origin of objects, even if you have only a few pieces remaining from the original.</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\">Investigation</strong>. When you inspect a damaged object, you gain knowledge of how it was damaged and how long ago.</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\">Mending</strong>. For 1 omni-gel, you can repair a single break or tear in an object, such as a punctured tire, a cracked helmet, or a ripped pack. As long as the break or tear is no larger than 30 cm (~ 1 foot) in any dimension, you mend it, leaving no trace of the former damage.</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\">Repair</strong>. You can restore 10 hit points to a damaged object for 1 omni-gel and an hour of work.</li>\n<li style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; break-inside: avoid;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;\">Craft Armor or Weapon Mod</strong>. See the&nbsp;<em style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Between Activities</em>section in chapter 8 for more information.</li>\n</ul>",
